1022
01:36:29,400 --> 01:36:34,280
To put it bluntly, people with his background were not wanted in the academic world of the 19th

1023
01:36:34,280 --> 01:36:37,880
century, and his parents had been under no illusions as to his chances.

1024
01:36:38,040 --> 01:36:44,040
His formal education ended when he was only 14, and instead of attending high school,

1025
01:36:44,040 --> 01:36:46,440
he was soon apprenticed as a banknote engraver.

1026
01:36:47,720 --> 01:36:52,520
During this apprenticeship, however, the young Smith became obsessed with biblical studies,

