01:37:53,240 --> 01:37:59,960
public. At first, he drew no attention, going ignored by the department's two members of permanent

1041
01:37:59,960 --> 01:38:05,240
staff. Eventually, however, they realized to their surprise that this young man could read

1042
01:38:05,240 --> 01:38:10,200
Kinneathorn better than any of themselves, and soon Rawinson would convince the museum

