and allusions in other tablets to similar legends. I therefore set about searching through the

1059
01:39:42,120 --> 01:39:47,560
collection. Commencing a steady search among these fragments, I soon found half of a curious

1060
01:39:47,560 --> 01:39:52,840
tablet which had evidently contained originally six columns of text. Two of these were still

1061
01:39:52,840 --> 01:39:57,800
nearly perfect, two others were imperfect, about half remaining, while the other remaining columns

1062
01:39:57,800 --> 01:40:03,480
