01:40:25,640 --> 01:40:29,000
although he made no mention of such an event in his own account.

1068
01:40:30,280 --> 01:40:33,640
Whether it happened or not, word of his discovery spread quickly.

1069
01:40:34,680 --> 01:40:39,240
As we mentioned before, the society of his time was one that was growing increasingly skeptical

1070
01:40:39,320 --> 01:40:44,840
about the literal truth of the Bible. It had only been 13 years since the publication of

1071
01:40:44,840 --> 01:40:49,160
Charles Darwin's On the Origin of Species, and by the time of Smith's discovery the

