the then Prime Minister William Gladstone, led to a immediate attention from the worldwide press.

1078
01:41:21,000 --> 01:41:25,960
Soon after, newspapers on either side of the Atlantic were trumpeting Smith's discovery,

1079
01:41:25,960 --> 01:41:29,800
and what they saw as its clear connections with the biblical story of Noah.

1080
01:41:30,760 --> 01:41:32,280
To quote the New York Times

1081
01:41:33,800 --> 01:41:38,760
